Name: Delicious Delights of Wondrous Wanderings
Desc: A dessert box based on the recipes of several different companions, simply overflowing with heartfelt intentions. The artisanry here is akin to the exquisite scene of the moon cutting through the clouds. Indeed, you can barely bear to eat such a precious gift.
Effect: Restores 34% of Max HP and an additional 1,900 HP to the selected character.
